      <title>私募股权不会停止借债偿还投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/private-equity-taps-leveraged-loans-to-pay-investors-in-dividend-recap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私募股权投资者迫切需要回报。满足他们要求的一种冒险方法是创下纪录并越来越受欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/private-equity-taps-leveraged-loans-to-pay-investors-in-dividend-recap</guid>
